n every hook invocation | Unlikely bottleneck but worth ruling out |\\n| 8 | **Transcript file size** | `user-prompt-submit` reads transcript for position | Large transcripts from long sessions |\\n| 9 | **Working tree dirty files** | `git status` in `user-prompt-submit` | Many uncommitted changes slow status |\\n\\nDimensions 1-2 we already benchmarked and they were flat. That suggests the **subprocess spawn + Go binary init + cobra + go-git PlainOpen** dominates at ~80ms and the actual hook logic is negligible in our synthetic repos.\\n\\nThe most likely culprits for a 10s startup are **5 (`.git/` pack size)** and **3+9 (worktree scan with many files/dirty state)** since those affect the fixed costs we can't avoid.\\n\\nWant me to update the benchmark to cover these additional dimensions?\"}],\"stop_reason\":null,\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":1,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":6194,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":95594,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":6194},\"output_tokens\":1,\"service_tier\":\"standard\",\"inference_geo\":\"not_available\"}},\"requestId\":\"req_011CYQ2QsCeRM56458Aq5RNu\",\"type\":\"assistant\",\"uuid\":\"8a535cda-4603-45eb-8c7a-d68745283bef\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-02-23T00:06:41.714Z\"}\n{\"parentUuid\":\"8a535cda-4603-45eb-8c7a-d68745283bef\",\"isSidechain\":false,\"userType\":\"external\",\"cwd\":\"/Users/evisdrenova/code/entire/devenv/cli\",\"sessionId\":\"960fa682-812c-41ee-859c-1136484fe07f\",\"version\":\"2.1.42\",\"gitBranch\":\"optimize_claude_start\",\"slug\":\"ancient-mixing-hearth\",\"type\":\"progress\",\"data\":{\"type\":\"hook_progress\",\"hookEvent\":\"Stop\",\"hookName\":\"Stop\",\"command\":\"go run ${CLAUDE_PROJECT_DIR}/cmd/entire/main.go hooks claude-code stop\"},\"parentToolUseID\":\"ffef798a-481b-48cd-87dc-0bd950cfd888\",\"toolUseID\":\"ffef798a-481b-48cd-87dc-0bd950cfd888\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-02-23T00:06:41.904Z\",\"uuid\":\"d12e67ed-2348-4610-b9f1-34d73493f1